title: EUR/USD Positive Outlook Holding Above First Support 1.1010/00
text:
EUR/USD And USD/CAD Spot Daily Forecast - October 16, 2019

EURUSD & USDCAD Spot Chart

outlook remains positive if we hold above first support at 1.1010/00 after the buy signal last week, initially targeting 1.1050/60 and 1.1075/85, perhaps as far as 1.1100/10.

Longs at 1.1010/00 need stops below 1.0980. An unexpected break below here kills the buy signal targeting 1.0950/40 and 1.0905/00 before the swing low at 1.0883/77.

holding above 1.3210 meets first resistance at 1.3230/40 but a break higher today meets a selling opportunity at 1.3270/80, with stops above 1.3300.

A break below 1.3190 retests last week's low at 1.3166. A break lower retests the September low at 1.3133/29 & below here targets 1.3105/00.
